Release Notes for Version 3.13.1
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.13.1 is the 2nd release in
the Errata Tool 3.13 development period. It closes [16 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes enabling multi-product advisories by
default, an API for viewing RPMDiff results, and several improvements and
fixes for docker image advisories.

